publisher			Ludosity							
publish_time	 2014年12月1日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Remedy, a recent graduate from the Saturnian healing school, must descend to Hurtland and use her powers to heal everyone from stray ducks to dark lords, and finally cure the ailing Prince Hingst. It's a short, whimsical adventure with plenty of heart(s).This game was one of Ludosity's entries in the Games Against Ebola charity game jam in 2014. This version was made after the jam to include options, multiple savefiles, more difficulty levels, and gamepad support.When using a gamepad, no setup is necessary - every button is used as the "action button".						
title	 Princess Remedy in a World of Hurt			
